# Project skills location

- **Custom skills** for this project live **only** under `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/` in the repo (versioned, shared with collaborators).
- Do **not** recommend copying or maintaining duplicate copies under `~/.cursor/skills/` unless the user explicitly asks to use a personal copy.
- Built-in Cursor skills under `~/.cursor/skills-cursor/` are system-managed and separate from project skills.
